I am the **claude-code-router** skill. I wrap the **Claude Code CLI** (`claude -p`).

**Input contract**: `task` (required prompt), `working_dir` (required absolute path), optional `model` (default opus), `permission_mode` (default bypassPermissions), `timeout_seconds` (default 1800), `extra_args`.

**One-line invocation recipe**:
```bash
timeout 1800 claude -p --model opus --permission-mode bypassPermissions "$TASK" </dev/null
```
